reviewText: Killing Machine was a decent Chiba flick (as far as Chiba movies go).  Shogun's Ninja would have been so much better without that horrible soundtrack, it sounded like 70's porn music.  I give this combo 4 stars within the realm of Chiba movies
come on you cant go wrong with a sonny chiba karate flick blood,n'guts over the top fights its really a great buy for its price
